		<title>Keeping it Simple in the Name of Clarity</title>
		<link>http://www.knanthony.com/blog/keeping-it-simple-in-the-name-of-clarity/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 15 Jan 2015 13:39:06 +0000</pubDate>
