<h4>Code Projects</h4>
[list list_style="orangePlus"]
<ul>
 	<li><a href="http://codepen.io/mikethomas/pen/nHfqA" target="_blank">Walking Cycle Using CSS Animations</a> | Mike Thomas</li>
 	<li><a href="http://tympanus.net/codrops/2013/06/18/caption-hover-effects/" target="_blank">Caption Hover Effects</a> | Mary Lou</li>
 	<li><a href="http://zurb.com/playground/twentytwenty" target="_blank">TwentyTwenty</a> (before and after slider) | Zurb Studios</li>
 	<li><a href="http://codepen.io/edankwan/pen/emqgpr" target="_blank">CSS Non-webgl realistic globe Demo</a> | Edan Kwan</li>
 	<li><a href="http://www.vincentbroute.fr/mapael/" target="_blank">Mapael Project</a> (interactive map) | Vincent Brout</li>
