		<content:encoded><![CDATA[I began the Daily UI 100 day challenge. Here's my Day 1 entry for a sign up page:

[column_one_third]

[lightbox media_type="image" thumbnail_url="http://www.knanthony.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Sign-Up-Page-576x1024.png" url="http://www.knanthony.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Sign-Up-Page-576x1024.png" width="100%" height="auto" align="left"][/lightbox]

&nbsp;

[/column_one_third]

[column_two_thirds_last]

Seems a simple task but the sign up page should be very simple for people to use AND only collect the information absolutely necessary. Those are important elements to think about.

[/column_two_thirds_last]]]></content:encoded>
