		<content:encoded><![CDATA[3rd week into my new job and I've got a ton to think about, especially as concerns xAPI and Caliper. Thinking maybe now's a good time to try installing an LRS at home?

What have you been making this week?

<!--more-->

This week, I've:

[list list_style="turquoisePlus"]
<ul>
	<li><strong>Adding</strong> a presentation layer to my Google Charts data viz using the bootstrap framework.</li>
	<li><strong>Automating</strong> the translation of the original clickstream data for the Google Charts using formulas in Excel. My first foray into using formulas!</li>
	<li><strong>Designing</strong> my first Free Code Camp front-end project, a one-page portfolio also built on the bootstrap framework. Take a look at the work-in-progress:<a href="http://codepen.io/anthkris/full/xwpPrE/" target="_blank">http://codepen.io/anthkris/full/xwpPrE/</a></li>
	<li><strong>Reading up</strong> on xAPI and the new Caliper spec.</li>
</ul>
[/list]]]></content:encoded>
