		<title>Dear Instructional Designer: A Sneak Peek at the new Show!</title>
		<link>http://www.knanthony.com/blog/dear-instructional-designer-a-sneak-peek-at-the-new-show/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 12 Apr 2016 12:12:33 +0000</pubDate>
