		<title>#DearID: Interview with Alyssa Gomez</title>
		<link>http://www.knanthony.com/blog/dearid-interview-with-alyssa-gomez/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 11 Aug 2016 12:15:30 +0000</pubDate>
