		<title>New #DearID: My Experience Creating with the Adapt Learning Framework</title>
		<link>http://www.knanthony.com/blog/new-dearid-my-experience-creating-with-the-adapt-learning-framework/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 29 Sep 2016 13:23:40 +0000</pubDate>
