		<title>#DearID: Interview with Hadiya Nuriddin</title>
		<link>http://www.knanthony.com/blog/dearid-interview-with-hadiya-nuriddin/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 17 Nov 2016 13:15:02 +0000</pubDate>
