	<item>
		<title>#DearID Episode 43: A Tale of Two Projects with Zsolt Olah</title>
		<link>http://www.knanthony.com/blog/dearid-episode-43-a-tale-of-two-projects-with-zsolt-olah/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 04 May 2017 12:11:04 +0000</pubDate>
